      "date": "2013-01-01 16:16:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/a071afdc-5429-11e2-b3ef-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
